I put this on my iPhone 11 13 days ago as of writing this review. The protector works very well and I feel much more comfortable putting my phone in my pocket with other things that could scratch it. Installation was pretty easy. I did get it slightly out of alighnment on my first attempt but luckily it wasn’t fully pressed down or anything so it peeled off and I tried again. I will say there are some smudges/streaks that seem to be on the underside of the protector HOWEVER I do not entirely blame the manufacturers because plenty of other variable could have contributed such as readjusting the protector not cleaning the phone good enough etc. I didn’t notice a decrease in camera quality. There might be a very slight decrease but let’s be honest you didn’t buy the iPhone 11 for the camera. All in all I recommend this project if you are as concerned about keeping your technology in great condition as I am.

The description said this product (camera lens protectors) was new.  When I received the package the outer envelope was completely sealed but the inner package - a small box - had been torn open. I tried to contact the seller but never got a response from one of the email addresses included in my order. I messaged the other email address and received a reply asking for a significant amount of personal info (not happening!).Hopefully I get the seller’s attention here and get the broken item replaced.Regarding the one good lens protector I received:  it seems to be of acceptable quality. It was a little hard to install because it needs to be perfectly straight to not interfere with the camera & flash. If it isn’t installed correctly it creates a terrible glare.  I put a toothpick in the hole in the protector to help hold it in place while I pressed it down on the phone.The adhesive seemed weak when I put the protector on but it hasn’t fallen off or slid. (It’s been installed for about a month).Update: lens protector shattered today. I didn’t drop my phone or bump it into anything I have no idea why it broke.  Don’t waste your time & money in this product find a better brand.

I am not happy with the type of product more than the item per se. As soon as you unpack it dust gets trapped on the glue. The glue is insufficiently sticky to keep it firmly in place when the phone is also dressed in a case. Finally the glass seems to be a fingerprint magnet - way more than the lenses. I would not recommend buying these types of products - your iPhone cameras will be fine so long as you have a case on your phone.
